## Features

- Modular i3blocks config with easy-to-add scripts
- Smart battery block with stepwise estimation and color coding
- RAM block with accurate percent and color feedback
- No blank spaces—always shows meaningful info
- Per-script documentation for deep understanding
- Easy to extend and adapt

