## Installation

```sh
git clone https://github.com/YOURUSERNAME/i3blocks-ultimate-setup.git
cp -r i3blocks-ultimate-setup/.config ~/
chmod +x ~/.config/i3blocks/scripts/*/*.sh
# Reload i3 or i3blocks as needed
```

